  "texts": [
    "The images consist of chest x-rays originating from Indiana University.",
    "Each report in the data set primarily encompasses multiple attributes such as comparison, indications, findings, and impressions.",
    "Reports with empty findings were excluded, resulting in 3337 remaining reports.",
    "Subsequently, we divided the remaining reports into training and testing sets in a 4:1 ratio, yielding 2668 reports for training and 669 reports for testing.The MIMIC-CXR data set was created by the Massachusetts Institute of Technology.",
    "The images are sourced from 65,379 patients who presented to the Beth Israel Deaconess Medical Center Emergency Department between 2011 and 2016."
  ],
